{"tid":2035041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應國安法 韓國瑜：希望香港社會和諧 和大陸和睦相處","createTime":"2020-05-25T15:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:16:12.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"b93de24178668026a9ff793da2809f1f4b206983","tid":2035041,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200524/1721550.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200524%2F1721550.htm&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e162d2a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200524/1721550.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸推「港版國安法」，香港民眾舉行「反惡歌法大遊行」回應，高雄市新聞局長鄭照新轉述高雄市長韓國瑜的說法：「國安法畢竟涉及香港社會敏感神經，呼籲謹慎為之。」<br />\n<br />\n記者詢問鄭照新，第一時間鄭照新強調：「國防外交兩岸等權責是中央層級，國民黨中央亦已對此議題發表聲明」，而韓國瑜市長做為直轄市長，現在是以市政為主，專注疫情、紓困、防災抗洪才是本分，不過呼籲：「香港高雄兩地，在商務、旅遊、農產貿易等友好往來密切，國安法畢竟涉及香港社會敏感神經，呼籲謹慎為之，充分尊重香港高度自治，避免破壞大陸與香港間互信基礎，以促進大陸與香港和睦相處，保障香港社會和諧為最高原則」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 港民抗議「港版國安法」大遊行 韓國瑜168字回應 | ETtoday政治 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200524/1721550.htm#ixzz6NT388Lt5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200524%2F1721550.htm%23ixzz6NT388Lt5&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=2f2b5f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200524/1721550.htm#ixzz6NT388Lt5</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"2a2ff773bdb2ad08dc0911a5537870531fdf33e9","tid":2035041,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"乜水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e2ca5903bb6d92bc831c1b337554698304f65f","tid":2035041,"uid":144372,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2a2ff773bdb2ad08dc0911a5537870531fdf33e9","tid":2035041,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":